content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8104.01 - City of Olean

State Regulations
(a) Route 16. The
northbound and southbound roadways of Route 16 between exit 26 of Route 17, the

Southern Tier Expressway, and Route 417. (b) Buffalo Street. The northwestbound and
southeastbound roadways of Buffalo Street between exit 25 of Route 17, the

Southern Tier Expressway, and Homer Road. (c) Homer Road. The northeastbound and
southwestbound roadways of Homer Road between Buffalo Street and Oregon

Road. (d) Oregon Road. The
northwestbound and southeastbound roadways of Oregon Road between Homer Road
and a point 500+- feet southeast of Homer Road. (e) South 19th Street. South 19th Street from

Route 417 to West Henley Street. Notes
